Laos Is Free of SARS - 2003-05-03
Laotian Prime Minister boun Nhang Vorachit declared his country free of the deadly disease that has affected many Asian nations in a meeting on SARS in Vientiane.  In another development, Laotian authorities are questioning three Hmong men suspected of involvement in a recent bus attack on Route 13 North.
